Top Nigerian riders company, Errand Junkie, has announced an empowerment program of a hire purchase opportunity for Nigerian riders willing to work for them. After a successful purchase of some brand new bikes, the company is calling for interview from interested Nigerians who are willing to be empowered. Errand Junkie is a 24 hour on-demand dispatch company. The brand’s mission is to be the industry’s most trusted customer-oriented errand service provider. To apply, call 0908 888 8009 for further details. Terms and conditions apply. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-859395 size-large" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG-20201216-WA0040-1024x695.jpg" alt="" width="740" height="502" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG-20201216-WA0040-1024x695.jpg 1024w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG-20201216-WA0040-300x204.jpg 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/IMG-20201216-WA0040.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px">